OL,3,CResidents 'ecstatic' as rural GP
OL,4,Csurgery saved from closure
OL,6,FThe future of a rural GP service has
OL,7,Fbeen saved by a new provider, who
OL,8,Fbelieves its model shows how
OL,9,Fhealthcare can be protected in rural
OL,10,Fareas.
OL,12,FEarlier this year, residents in a
OL,13,FCumbrian town had feared their GP
OL,14,Fsurgery may close after an advert to
OL,15,Ffind a new doctor received no
OL,16,Fapplications.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
