FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1780989358
OL,3,CResidents 'ecstatic' as rural GP
OL,4,Csurgery saved from closure
OL,6,FThe previous GP in Coniston stopped
OL,7,Foperating in August 2025, after being
OL,8,Frun by a family doctor for 170 years.
OL,9,FWhen the previous GP retired, a
OL,10,Ftemporary service had been running and
OL,11,Fwas due to end in March.
OL,13,FHoping to not see their local surgery
OL,14,Fclosed down for good, residents
OL,15,Fcreated a video advert to try and
OL,16,Fattract people to the area, and even
OL,17,Flaunched a petition to keep GP
OL,18,Fservices in the town, which received
OL,19,Fmore than 1,000 signatures.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1780989358
OL,3,CResidents 'ecstatic' as rural GP
OL,4,Csurgery saved from closure
OL,6,FCumbria Health will take over as the
OL,7,Fnew provider on July 1, 2026.
OL,9,FIt says that being a larger
OL,10,Forganisation already operating other
OL,11,Fnearby surgeries means they can move
OL,12,Fresources around to run smaller
OL,13,Fbranches like Coniston with less money.
OL,15,FFor residents like Doreen Phoenix,
OL,16,Fknowing Coniston will still have a GP
OL,17,Fcomes as a huge relief, because she
OL,18,Fsays it was a key factor in her moving
OL,19,Fto the area.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1780989358
OL,3,CResidents 'ecstatic' as rural GP
OL,4,Csurgery saved from closure
OL,6,FShe said: "I had a heart attack. My
OL,7,Fhusband had a big stroke 16 years ago
OL,8,Fand he's had a couple of smaller ones
OL,9,Fsince, so it was important that we
OL,10,Fwere able to get into the NHS services
OL,11,Fquickly.
OL,13,F"We did consider that the hospitals
OL,14,Fare a bit further away. So we needed a
OL,15,Fdoctor very close at hand. In the
OL,16,Fwinter the weather can get bad and we
OL,17,Fcan get blocked in.
OL,19,F"Also in the summer, the amount of
OL,20,Ftraffic on the road with the tourists,
OL,21,Fit's hard to get anywhere."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1780989358
OL,3,CResidents 'ecstatic' as rural GP
OL,4,Csurgery saved from closure
OL,6,FSpeaking about Cumbria Health taking
OL,7,Fover the surgery, Doreen added: "This
OL,8,Fis more than just a yes, thank you
OL,9,Fvery much. We are ecstatic in this
OL,10,Fvillage."
OL,12,FFrom the 1st of July, the surgery will
OL,13,Fbe open three days a week, providing
OL,14,Fface to face appointments.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1780989358
OL,3,CResidents 'ecstatic' as rural GP
OL,4,Csurgery saved from closure
OL,6,FRoss Brand, the Chief Executive of
OL,7,FCumbria Health said: "So you will
OL,8,Fsometimes see a nurse, nurse
OL,9,Fpractitioner, a paramedic
OL,10,Fpractitioner, a pharmacist,
OL,11,Fphysiotherapist or a doctor. But all
OL,12,Fof our clinical services are overseen
OL,13,Fby medical professionals."
OL,15,FWhen questioned about its financially
OL,16,Fstability and if it is going to stay,
OL,17,FMr Brand added: "Absolutely.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1780989358
OL,3,CResidents 'ecstatic' as rural GP
OL,4,Csurgery saved from closure
OL,6,F"We recognise it's been a challenged
OL,7,Fsurgery to operate. Our organisation
OL,8,Fis about doing the right thing for
OL,9,FCumbria. So this was a hard problem
OL,10,Ffor many people to try and solve. And
OL,11,Fas long as we're open to work with the
OL,12,Fcommunity and innovating, we'll make
OL,13,Fthis work.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1780989358
OL,3,CResidents 'ecstatic' as rural GP
OL,4,Csurgery saved from closure
OL,6,F"When you're providing services for a
OL,7,Fthousand people, you get the same
OL,8,Famount of money for that thousand
OL,9,Fpeople as if they are one of 10,000,
OL,10,For they're one of 1000. By joining
OL,11,Fforces with other smaller practices,
OL,12,Fdoing things at scale together, like
OL,13,Fanswering the telephones, like doing
OL,14,Fworkflow administration, we can just
OL,15,Fmake that NHS pound go a bit further."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
